REM *** LESSON 41: SMOOTH SCROLLING TEXT ***
REM Practical Example
10 REM *** SCROLLING MESSAGE ***
20 PRINT CHR$(147)
30 MS$="*** WELCOME TO THE C64 ***"
40 MS$=MS$+SPACE$(40)
50 POKE 53270,PEEK(53270)OR16
60 P=1
70 FOR S=0 TO 7
80 POKE 53270,(PEEK(53270)AND240)OR S
